  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (synthetic adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial sample declares assuranceLevel Medium despite multiple credibility factors achieving levels below required levels, triggering COMPOUND-03 (assurance-level overstatement). The decision record records Accepted, compounding the inconsistency.",
