      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison of model predictions to experimental measurements using formal metric (e.g., E_rel or MAPE) with uncertainty bounds at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index predictions compared to experimental values at 3 operating points. Mean absolute error is 28%, exceeding the 15% threshold required for Gradation 4. Uncertainty bounds overlap at 2 of 3 points. No formal validation metric computed. Achieved level 2 against required level 4.",
