      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on prior literature. Single turbulence model used; no comparison to RSM or LES performed. Hemolysis power-law exponents taken from Giersiepen 1990 without uncertainty bounds on coefficients. Model form uncertainty not formally quantified. Achieved level 2 against required level 5."
    },
